State.Description: Adds some of the outfits of your favorite traders as usable armor. This is the first armor pack mod that allows automatic switching between male/female outfit depending on the gender of your player character. Includes custom, unique and improved armor bonuses for a more fun gameplay.

State.Author: LittleRedSonja
State.Description: Adds 5 completely new and superior female/unisex armors to the game, in a tactical fashion: 2 light, 3 medium. High quality models and textures. Custom bonuses. Compatible with V1 and V2 of the game. Compatible with the new cosmetic system introduced in 2.0. Built - in support for Escape from Tarkov.
State.Name: LittleRedSonja and Mumpfy ArmorPack05 TactiGirls

State.Description: Adds 4 new custom armors to the game, for male and female with gender auto-switch, inspired by The Walking Dead. Light and medium armors. High quality models and textures. Custom bonuses. Compatible with V1 and V2 of the game or later. Compatible with the new cosmetic system introduced in 2.0. Built - in support for Escape from Tarkov and Rebirth.
State.Name: LittleRedSonja and Mumpfy ArmorPack07 The Walking Dead

State.Author: Mumpfy and LittleRedSonja
State.Description: Welcome to Halloweeny, where the scary meets the cute! This mod adds several variants of masks, hats, helmets and full body outfits, decorative blocks, lights, workbenches, witchy cauldrons, all inspired by the spooky season. Enjoy Halloween in your game like never before! Treat or Trick!
State.Name: Halloweeny

State.Author: LittleRedSonja
State.Description: Add a new vehicle, the Barbie Davidson Motorcycle. 6 mod slots, Big Storage and fuel capacity, Better speed and maneuverability. Custom visuals for all the installable vehicle mods and Custom real Harley Davidson sounds. Compatible with V1 and V2 of the game. Compatible with the vast majority of other mods and overhauls.
State.Name: LittleRedSonja Barbie Davidson Vehicle

State.Author: LittleRedSonja
State.Description: This support mod allows integration of custom armors and outfits included in other mods in the new cosmetics/wardrobe system. Support already included for all our armor mods and Winterween armors, and I will add support and develop the mod to allow for other custom armors to be included.
State.Name: LittleRedSonja Cosmetic Armor System (CAS)

State.Author: LittleRedSonja
State.Description: This mod is intended to add and improve decorations for your bases, in the form of new pickupable items, new crafting recipes, and add some additional functionality to some of the decoration items in the game
State.Name: Fancy Home Deco

State.Author: LittleRedSonja
State.Description: A small mod that adds 24 Fallout Vault-Tec posters in "New" and "Old" style variants. All craftable, ready to decorate your Vault.

State.Author: LittleRedSonja
State.Description: A mighty Tractor vehicle I made for some friends. You can dye it with your favorite color. It includes custom mods for Super Charger, Light mod, Fuel Reserve mod, and Plow, but can also equip all the other mods up to 5 in total. Custom horn sound. Craftable in the workbench. The mod is for V1 or later versions of 7 days to die.
State.Name: LittleRedSonja Farmer Sage Tractor Vehicle

State.Author: LittleRedSonja
State.Description: Makes the Chainsaw into a weapon of mass destruction when wearing lumberjack set, increasing damage, damage resistance, fuel capacity and attack speed. Tweaked stats to make it as balanced as possible while making the chainsaw powerful and fun to use. Become the king of badassery in the zombie apocalypse!
State.Name: Navezgane Chainsaw Massacre

State.Author: LittleRedSonja
State.Description: Adds 45 cute Plushies for you to decorate your base or bring with you in your adventures. They can all be placed on top of ANY surface, at any level. You can pick them up after being placed. All are craftable in the workbench, no skill unlock required. Version 1.1.0 added a "Catch them All" minigame and an optional "Loot Only" mode.
State.Name: LittleRedSonja Plushies

State.Author: LittleRedSonja
State.Description: A 74-Z Speeder Bike vehicle from Star Wars movies. Very fast and with high maneuverability it can easily hover over obstacles and cross over rivers, lakes and canyons. 2 versions of the vehicle included. It includes custom sounds from the movies, custom visuals for all the vehicle mods and new ingredients. May The Force be with you!
State.Name: LittleRedSonja StarWars Speeder Bike Vehicle

State.Author: LittleRedSonja

They are lootable if you are using EFTX mod.
